/p> \n<br> <p>This is also the time to stock up on accessories that make a difference in day-to-day use. <b>Shop siren speakers, wiring harness kits,</b> and <b>emergency light controllers,</b> all available at limited-time discounts. We haven't forgotten our first responder community either — you'll also find savings on <b>police car lights, ambulance lights, firefighter lights,</b> and <b>volunteer firefighter lights.</b> No matter what you drive — <b>a tow truck, construction vehicle,</b> or <b>utility truck</b> — our Black Friday sale delivers professional-grade equipment at the lowest prices of the year. Don't wait — once these deals are gone, they won't return until next year.</p>\n</div>"
